<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="https://overfload.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/ed485a58-4e11-4940-9b58-9dafd0113a9d">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8"/>
	    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
	    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>

	    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"/>
	    <script style="display: none" src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.1.2/dist/ionicons.js"></script>

		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/front.css"/>

		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<title>⚪ Sparks</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div style="position: absolute; top: 20px" class="spark-logo">
				<a href="https://summerspark.stab.org"></a>
			</div>

			<div class="balance">
				<h1 class="shake_balance animate__animated">23.45</h1>
				<h1 class="shake_balance animate__animated">1205.367</h1>
				<span class="lightning-bolt">⚡</span>
				<h1 id="balance_display" class="animate__animated">{{BALANCE}}</h1>
			</div>

			<div class="select-icons">
				<div class="icon-div open-inventory">
					<ion-icon class="icon-objects" name="file-tray-stacked-outline"></ion-icon>

				</div>
				<div class="icon-div send-item">
					<ion-icon class="icon-objects" name="send-outline"></ion-icon>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="inventory-popup">
				<h1>Current Inventory</h1>
				<div class="close-inventory">
					<ion-icon class="icon-objects" name="close-circle-outline"></ion-icon>
				</div>
				<div class="inner-inventory">
					<div id="initial-inventory">
						<div class="display-styling-inventory">
							<div style="background-image: url('https://overfload.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/ed485a58-4e11-4940-9b58-9dafd0113a9d');" class="spark-logo-inventory"></div>
							<div class="item-info">
								<div style="display: inline;" class="item-name">Ball</div>
								<ion-icon name="chevron-forward-outline"></ion-icon>
								<div style="display: inline;" class="seller">Head</div>
							</div>
							<button class="purchase-item">
								<span class="lightning-bolt-button">⚡</span>
								<span class="price">20</span>
							</button>
						</div>

						<div class="inventory-descript">
							Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur sed arcu et urna accumsan mollis. Aliquam vitae nibh libero. Maecenas a neque vitae eros fringilla scelerisque id non nisi. Phasellus diam est, aliquet nec auctor varius, condimentum a erat. Praesent imperdiet lacus ipsum, id tristique libero volutpat sed. Etiam eget accumsan tellus, eu consectetur felis. Proin rutrum metus eu justo fermentum, faucibus porttitor velit gravida. Sed nisi ligula, condimentum sit amet nisl vel, fermentum venenatis mauris. Duis non eros placerat, commodo justo at, volutpat ligula. Cras sodales lacinia risus ut suscipit. Nulla semper in nibh ut pretium.
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="send-item-popup">
				<h1>Send Sparks</h1>
				<div class="close-send-item">
					<ion-icon class="icon-objects" name="close-circle-outline"></ion-icon>
				</div>

				<form method="POST" action="/nowhere">
					<input type="text" name="receiver_id" placeholder="Receiver's ID" pattern="[0-9]+">
					<input type="text" name="number" placeholder="Amount">
					<input type="text" name="message" placeholder="Message">
					<input type="submit" value="Send" id="submission">
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>

		<script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
		<script src="/initial.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>